1900-01-01 CCTC: Enrollment Prerequisite 2564 POINTER
SELECT srr.ITEM_R_STATUS , rq.DESCR FROM %Table(SSR_REQS_RSLTS) srr , %Table(TERM_TBL) trm , %Table(RQ_GRP_TBL) rq , %Table(CLASS_TBL) cls WHERE srr.INSTITUTION = :4 AND srr.ACAD_CAREER = :5 AND srr.EMPLID = :1 AND srr.SSR_REQS_TYPE = 'E' AND srr.ENTRY_R_TYPE = 'KEYRQG' AND srr.SSR_ENTRY_SEQ = ( SELECT MAX(ssr_ES.SSR_ENTRY_SEQ) FROM %Table(SSR_REQS_RSLTS) ssr_ES WHERE ssr_ES.EMPLID = srr.EMPLID AND ssr_ES.ACAD_CAREER = srr.ACAD_CAREER AND ssr_ES.INSTITUTION = srr.INSTITUTION AND ssr_ES.STRM = srr.STRM AND ssr_ES.CLASS_NBR = srr.CLASS_NBR AND ssr_ES.SSR_REQS_TYPE = srr.SSR_REQS_TYPE AND ssr_ES.SSR_REQS_SEQ_NO = srr.SSR_REQS_SEQ_NO AND ssr_ES.ENTRY_R_TYPE = srr.ENTRY_R_TYPE) AND srr.STRM = trm.STRM AND (%DateIn(LTRIM(:2)) BETWEEN trm.TERM_BEGIN_DT AND trm.TERM_END_DT) AND srr.RQRMNT_GROUP = rq.RQRMNT_GROUP AND rq.EFF_STATUS = 'A' AND rq.EFFDT = ( SELECT MAX(rq_ED.EFFDT) FROM %Table(RQ_GRP_TBL) rq_ED WHERE rq_ED.RQRMNT_GROUP = rq.RQRMNT_GROUP AND rq_ED.EFFDT <= trm.TERM_BEGIN_DT) AND srr.INSTITUTION = cls.INSTITUTION AND srr.ACAD_CAREER = cls.ACAD_CAREER AND srr.STRM = cls.STRM AND srr.CLASS_NBR = cls.CLASS_NBR AND (LTRIM(RTRIM(cls.SUBJECT)) %Concat '-' %Concat LTRIM(RTRIM(cls.CATALOG_NBR))) = :3

POINTER
GBL 32
1900-01-01 CCTC Student Enrollments Get 2118 POINTER
SELECT A.EMPLID , A.STRM , A.CLASS_NBR , A.STDNT_ENRL_STATUS , A.STATUS_DT , A.UNT_TAKEN , A.GRADING_BASIS_ENRL , A.AUDIT_GRADE_BASIS , A.CRSE_GRADE_OFF , A.GRADE_DT , (LTRIM(RTRIM(B.SUBJECT)) %Concat '-' %Concat LTRIM(RTRIM(B.CATALOG_NBR))) , B.DESCR , C.LAST_ATTEND_DT FROM %Table(STDNT_ENRL) A JOIN %Table(CLASS_TBL) B ON (A.INSTITUTION = B.INSTITUTION AND A.ACAD_CAREER = B.ACAD_CAREER AND A.STRM = B.STRM AND A.CLASS_NBR = B.CLASS_NBR) LEFT OUTER JOIN ( SELECT ATT.EMPLID , ATT.STRM , ATT.CLASS_NBR , ATT.INSTITUTION , ATT.ACAD_CAREER , MAX(ATT.CLASS_ATTEND_DT) AS LAST_ATTEND_DT FROM %Table(CLASS_ATTENDNCE) ATT WHERE ATT.CLASS_ATTEND_DT IS NOT NULL GROUP BY ATT.EMPLID, ATT.STRM, ATT.CLASS_NBR, ATT.INSTITUTION, ATT.ACAD_CAREER) C ON (A.EMPLID = C.EMPLID AND A.STRM = C.STRM AND A.CLASS_NBR = C.CLASS_NBR AND A.INSTITUTION = C.INSTITUTION AND A.ACAD_CAREER = C.ACAD_CAREER) WHERE A.EMPLID LIKE :1 AND A.STRM LIKE :2 AND A.CLASS_NBR LIKE :3 AND A.INSTITUTION = :4 AND A.ACAD_CAREER = :5
